Description: "Herbal Roots Herbal Henna Powder is a 100% Natural and Herbal beauty product. It comes with the goodness of different herbs that are known to give great shine and health to hair. Herbal Roots henna powder is a concoction of a lot of ingredients that are extremely beneficial for hair growth and healthy hair and are widely used in Ayurveda for treating hair and scalp problems. It is used to color your hair in a natural way. Henna hair color is not only safe and quick, but also without any harmful side effects. Applying Herbal Roots Henna Pack twice a month will make the hair glossy, healthy and voluminous. It acts as a good conditioner for your hair and helps it grow faster. It promotes hair growth, reduces hair fall, dandruff and other scalp problems. How to Use: Take henna powder, measured according to the length of your hair. Add a solution enriched with Vitamin C (lemon or any citrus fruit juice) which will give bounce to your hair and is an effective dandruff treatment. (optional) Add cold water to the mixture to make a paste-like consistency. For moisturizing your hair you can also add yogurt, eggs or olive oil. This will nourish the scalp in a gentle manner. (Optional) Leave the mixture aside in the refrigerator for some time. Apply it over the scalp with the help of a brush. You may apply it with your hands too, but that could result in your fingertips getting coloured with the henna. Let the mixture dry for a span of forty five minutes to one hour. (or more if you wish to use it for coloring your hair). Wash off with a non-drying shampoo. "

Title: Playboy Play It Lovely EDT  -  75 ml(For Women)
Description: Tantalizing and refreshing, Playboy Play It Lovely is made for the woman who sends across shock waves with a passing glance. Her playful nature doesn’t overshadow her sophisticated aura. This Eau de Toilette complements the woman who effortlessly juggles elegance and flirtation. Fresh and zesty notes of citrus along with rich hints of blackberry and fruity extracts of pear that join hands to produce a sweet-scented top note. This is followed by an aromatic mix of sweet and heady belle de nuit, cherry baby orchid that exudes hints of chocolate and green tuberose. Ending with a base note of smoky amber, earthy patchouli and tonka bean which is a potpourri of aromas, add a sensuous nuance to the perfume. This enticing fragrance makes a lasting impression no matter what time you choose to wear it. The delicate glass vial that holds this scent radiates a feminine charm and the black cap in the shape of bunny ears with a bow puts the stamp of Playboy. The soft and powdery pink shade of the perfume radiates through the glass vial. Playboy Play It Lovely is the trademark scent of the woman who is innocently playful and at ease with all the attention.

Description: The delicate innocence of freshly blossomed spring flowers, freedom of walking barefoot on grass and the splendour of kissing in the rain - Benetton’s Let's Love EDT is a playful feminine fragrance that evokes a warm, happy feeling called love. This splendid floral fragrance is for the modern young woman who dreams of the miracle of romance. Let’s Love opens with light top notes of bamboo sap, pineapple and lily of the valley bells that give way to heart notes of succulent raspberry, passion flower and star jasmine. The delicate fragrance finally settles into warm and sensual base notes of cedarwood, cashmere wood and caressing musk. Envelop yourself with the playful, bright and irresistible charm of Benetton’s Let’s Love EDT and embrace your girly side.
